Preconditions:
The batchSize parameter must be a positive integer.
The groups array must not be null.
The groups array must contain at least one element.
Each element in the groups array must be a positive integer.

Postconditions:
The method should return an integer representing the maximum possible number of happy groups.
The groups array may be rearranged to maximize the number of happy groups.
The order of the groups array may be changed.
The original groups array should not be modified.
The returned value should be greater than or equal to 0.